The realme 12 Pro+ maximizes the potential of the telephoto lens by not only taking it further than ever, with 3X optical zoom and 6X in-sensor zoom, but by producing results comparable to that of main cameras at optical focal lengths, with the same quality, consistency, and reliability.

[{'Reviewer': 'Pritam Shetty', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in India on 30 September 2023', 'Review': "I recently made the switch from Android to the iPhone 14 Plus, and it has been a remarkably smooth transition. Here are some key points about my experience:

1. Seamless Setup: Setting up my new iPhone was a breeze. Apple's migration tool effortlessly transferred all my contacts, photos, and apps from my Android device. It was a stress-free process that ensured I didn't lose any important data.

2. Intuitive User Interface: The iOS interface on the iPhone 14 Plus is incredibly user-friendly. Navigating through the device, customizing settings, and finding apps is straightforward, even for someone who was accustomed to Android.

3. Performance: The iPhone 14 Plus packs a powerful punch. The device runs smoothly, and apps load quickly. Multitasking is a breeze, thanks to the robust hardware and optimized software.

4. Display: The OLED display on the iPhone 14 Plus is stunning. Colors are vibrant, and the screen is sharp and clear. It's a joy to use for watching videos, browsing, and gaming.

5. Camera: The camera quality on the iPhone 14 Plus is exceptional. The photos and videos captured are rich in detail and clarity. The advanced camera features and modes provide ample opportunities for creativity.

6. App Ecosystem: The App Store offers a vast selection of high-quality apps that enhance the iPhone experience. I found all my favorite Android apps and discovered some excellent iOS exclusives.

7. Privacy and Security: Apple's commitment to user privacy and security is evident. Features like App Tracking Transparency and Face ID add an extra layer of protection.

8. Battery Life: The battery life on the iPhone 14 Plus is impressive. I can comfortably go through a day of heavy usage without worrying about running out of power.

In conclusion, my transition from Android to the iPhone 14 Plus has been a positive one. The next-gen imaging in the realme 12 Pro Series was made for cinematic portrait shots. We specifically tuned the imaging in the realme 12 Pro Series for true-to-life results, with great color and clarity, and for a dramatic cinematic effect with great texture.

Title: Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max Sim (256 GB) - Natural Titanium
Description:
About this item
FORGED IN TITANIUM — iPhone 15 Pro Max has a strong and light aerospace-grade titanium design with a textured matt-glass back. It also features a super-tough Ceramic Shield front. And it’s splash, water and dust resistant.
ADVANCED DISPLAY — The 6.7 Super Retina XDR display2 with ProMotion ramps up refresh rates to 120Hz when you need exceptional graphics performance. Dynamic Island bubbles up alerts and Live Activities. Plus, with Always-On display, your Lock Screen stays glanceable, so you don’t have to tap it to stay in the know.
GAME-CHANGING A17 PRO CHIP — A Pro-class GPU makes mobile games feel so immersive, with rich environments and realistic characters. A17 Pro is also incredibly efficient and helps to deliver amazing all-day battery life.
POWERFUL PRO CAMERA SYSTEM — Get incredible framing flexibility with 7 pro lenses. Capture super high resolution photos with more colour and detail using the 48MP Main camera. And take sharper close-ups from further away with the 5x Telephoto camera on iPhone 15 Pro Max.
CUSTOMISABLE ACTION BUTTON — Action button is a fast track to your favourite feature. Just set the one you want, like Silent mode, Camera, Voice Memo, Shortcut and more. Then press and hold to launch the action.
PRO CONNECTIVITY — The new USB-C connector lets you charge your Mac or iPad with the same cable you use to charge iPhone 15 Pro Max. With USB 3, you get a huge leap in data transfer speeds.4 And you can download files up to 2x faster using Wi-Fi 6E.
VITAL SAFETY FEATURES — If you need emergency services and you don’t have mobile service or Wi-Fi, you can use Emergency SOS via satellite.6 With Crash Detection, iPhone can detect a serious car crash and call for help if you can’t.

[{'Reviewer': 'Darvy Guerrero', 'Rating': '1.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in the United States on 27 June 2024', 'Review': 'Phone’s camera is not working'}, {'Reviewer': 'Cliente Amazon', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Spain on 30 August 2024', 'Review': 'Llevo meses ya con el tele y debo decir que estoy totalmente satisfecho con él.
Va como un tiro, no me ha dado ni un problema y la cámara es una maravilla.
En cuanto a rendimiento, ninguna queja. Lo mueve todo sin problemas, incluso con muchas aplicaciones abiertas.
De memoria va más que sobrado, así que el hecho de no tener tarjeta de ampliación no me afecta.
La cámara, como he dicho, es una pasada. Gran resolución, muy configurable y con un zoom alucinante. El estabilizador funciona de maravilla también.
El sonido es muy bueno también, con el dolby.
Las únicas pegas que le encuentro son que la vibración es muy suave y a veces no me entero cuando llega algo y está en ese modo, que las notificaciones no suenan muy fuerte, (aunque el tono de llamada sí), y que al conectado al PC, como todos los realme, se pone a buscar fotos de forma automática y tardas un poco en poder manejarte entre las carpetas.
Sin tres pujada, pero por lo demás, estoy encantado con el teléfono.'}, {'Reviewer': 'Salex', 'Rating': '4.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Italy on 24 July 2024', 'Review': "Ho provato questo smartphone poiché era molto apprezzato nella fascia di prezzo 300/400 Euro, che è quella che mi intèressa.
Ecco le mie impressioni dopo alcuni giorni di utilizzo:

**Design e Costruzione:**
Il telefono si presenta bene e solido. Esteticamente, non amo il comparto fotografico così invadente al centro, ma sono solo gusti personali.

**Autonomia:**
Arrivando da un Samsung S23 che non mi permetteva di terminare la giornata con una sola carica, questo device è una piacevole sorpresa. Utilizzandolo intensamente, riesce a coprire un'intera giornata senza problemi. Acceso dalle 8 di mattina, arriva facilmente alle 23 con ancora un 15-20% di carica residua e quasi 6 ore di schermo attivo.

**Prestazioni:**
La fluidità è discreta e non presenta impuntamenti significativi. Le prestazioni generali sono adeguate per la fascia di prezzo.

**Fotocamera:**
Il comparto fotografico sa il fatto suo, anche nelle foto con scarsa illuminazione. Sebbene non sia il top di gamma, le foto risultano comunque di buona qualità per un telefono di questa fascia.

**Connettività:**
Ottimo il segnale telefonico; il dispositivo prende molto bene anche in posti dove i miei precedenti device stentavano a restare connessi.

**Display:**
Il display è ottimo anche alla luce del sole, rendendo facile l'utilizzo all'aperto.

**Ricarica:**
Molto comoda la ricarica ultra veloce, che in meno di un'ora abbondante porta la batteria al 100%.

**Punti di Critica:**
Non sarebbe stato male se fosse stato un po' più leggero e magari più sottile, ma non si può avere tutto. L'unico vero problema riscontrato è stato con il vivavoce: molti amici mi hanno detto che mi sentivano male, anche con il telefono vicino alla bocca.

**Conclusioni:**
Detto questo, se l'estetica delle fotocamere vi piace, è un telefono davvero tuttofare. Per la fascia di prezzo, offre un ottimo rapporto qualità-prezzo e soddisfa le esigenze quotidiane con efficacia.
Read more"}, {'Reviewer': 'Nicola', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Italy on 14 August 2024', 'Review': 'Ottimo smartphone. Il sistema operativo è privo di bug. Il materiale con cui è costruito è molto buono. Lo schermo curvo pensavo desse fastidio e invece no. Le foto sono molto belle, non perfette ma se la cava molto bene in ogni situazione. Batteria di lunga durata'}, {'Reviewer': 'Enzo', 'Rating': '4.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Italy on 10 August 2024', 'Review': "Tutto perfetto 'unica pecca quando chiamo o mi chiamano l'audio mi sembra un po' basso, qualcuno di voi a trovato lo stesso mio problema e se si come lì ha risolto?"}]

reviews:
[{'Reviewer': 'Ertan Dursun', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Turkey on 29 July 2024', 'Review': "Bu bütçeyle alınabilecek güzel bir telefon olduğu aşikar ancak fiyat/performans bir telefon olduğunu düşünmüyorum. Fiyatı neyse onu veriyor.

Telefon aslında 2023 yılının Kasım ayında Çin'e özel olarak çıkan Redmi K70'in global versiyonu. Yani yeni bir cihaz olmasına rağmen o kadar da yeni olmadığını söyleyeyim.

Normal kullanımda şu sıcaklarda bile bir ısınma görmedim. Batarya sıcaklığı 40 derecenin üstünü görmüyor. Squad Busters gibi basit bir oyunda 40 derece civarında seyrederken Warzone gibi ağır bir oyun oynadığınızda ise 45 dereceleri görüyor. Bu piyasada araştırdığım bütün telefonlarda böyle. Çünkü hem telefonlar güçlü hem de oyunlar çok ağır.

Yazılımında herhangi bir takılma vs. yok ki bu durum beni daha önceden 3 Xiaomi cihaz daha kullanmış biri olarak epey şaşırttı. Çünkü yazılım konusunda çokça şikayet edilen bir marka bildiğiniz üzere.

Ekranı oldukça kaliteli. Samsung S23 Ultra ile yan yana koyduğumda gözüme biraz daha iyi geldi ama eşit diyebilirim.

Bataryası %0-100 arasını ortalama 25-30 dakikada tamamlıyor. Firmanın iddia ettiği gibi normal şartlar altında 19 dakikada dolum söz konusu değil ama ciddi bir fark da yok. Çok tatmin ettiğini söyleyebilirim. Ayrıca bataryası normal uygulamaların yoğun kullanımında bile bir günü çok rahat çıkartıyor. Ağır oyunlar oynandığında bir günü çıkarabileceğini zannetmiyorum ama zaten 25-30 dakikada doluyor olması bunu bir sorun olmaktan çıkarıyor benim gözümde. 120w max. şarj etme modunda batarya 42-45 derecelere ulaşıyor. Havanın da sıcak olmasının etkisi yadsınamaz tabi ki. Ekran süresini merak edecekler için ortalamada 8-10 saat ekran süresini 24 saatlik süre içerisinde alabiliyorsunuz. Tabi ki bu durum sadece internette gezinme, sosyal medya, youtube gibi platformların kullanıldığı durumda geçerli.

Ben telefonu almadan önce çok fazla araştırmama rağmen bazı bilgileri, özellikle de ekran süresi konusunda, bulamamıştım. Umarım telefonu almak isteyenler için bu yorum faydalı olur.

1. التصميم والجودة:
من اللحظة الأولى التي استلمت فيها جيراسول G30، لاحظت الجودة العالية في التصنيع. التصميم أنيق وعصري، والمادة المستخدمة متينة وتشعر بالصلابة. التفاصيل الدقيقة في التصميم تعكس اهتمام الشركة بالجودة.

2. الأداء:
الأداء كان ممتازاً بكل المقاييس. سواء كنت أستخدم المنتج للعمل أو الترفيه، كنت دائماً مسروراً بسرعة الاستجابة والكفاءة العالية. لم أواجه أي مشكلة في الأداء حتى عند استخدامه لفترات طويلة.

3. سهولة الاستخدام:
جيراسول G30 سهل الاستخدام للغاية. الإعدادات بديهية وواضحة، مما يجعل من السهل على أي شخص البدء في استخدامه فوراً دون الحاجة إلى دليل معقد. الواجهة المستخدم سهلة التصفح وتوفر تجربة مريحة.

4. الميزات:
المنتج يأتي مع مجموعة واسعة من الميزات التي تلبي جميع احتياجاتي. من الميزات الإضافية الذكية إلى الخصائص الأساسية، جيراسول G30 يوفر كل ما أحتاجه وأكثر. الميزات المدمجة تعمل بشكل سلس وتجعل من استخدام المنتج تجربة ممتعة.

5. القيمة مقابل السعر:
مع كل هذه الميزات والجودة العالية، أرى أن جيراسول G30 يوفر قيمة ممتازة مقابل السعر. إنه استثمار ذكي لأي شخص يبحث عن منتج متين وموثوق.

Its unique , price is affordable, i dont mind not having 3 lens camera i have the most unique pink color of iphone 2021💞📱 the pictures are great by the way even if its not 3 lens 😄 💞💞💞💞💞'}, {'Reviewer': 'ぽこニャン2号', 'Rating': '4.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Japan on 1 May 2022', 'Review': '11プロが壊れたので13にしようと思いました。どうせなら
ポイントも増えるとアマゾンで買いましたが。
欲しい色は256Gでした。よく見たら128Gはピンクしか

購入後に来た専用申し込みURLがのっているメールにある「エントリーコード」とは、いつ使うのか？使う時があるのか？
キャンペーンのページを見てもよく分からなかったので、Amazonサポートに電話して聞きました。かなり長く待たされた後の答え→「専用URLの申し込みページから申し込めば“2万円キャンペーン”は適用になります。」とのこと。
それでは、何のためにエントリーコードが記載されているのか？･･･という素朴な疑問は横に置いて、申し込みを完了させました。

iPhone13は軽くてとても満足しています。11からの変更ですが、マスク付き顔認証がほしかったので。コツはあるけど、使ってみてやはり便利でした。'}]

والذي يعتبر اضعف كثيراً من ال5G'}, {'Reviewer': 'Mohamed Sameh', 'Rating': '1.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Egypt on 25 November 2023', 'Review': 'مش نفس اللون'}, {'Reviewer': 'Ekramy', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Egypt on 21 November 2023', 'Review': 'جميل'}, {'Reviewer': 'ahmed elbaz', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Egypt on 3 September 2023', 'Review': 'منتج ممتاز'}, {'Reviewer': 'Valeria', 'Rating': '1.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in the United States on 14 April 2024', 'Review': "I purchased this phone more than 4month ago and unfortunately, my experience with it has been quite disappointing. Here's my honest review:

**Performance:** The performance of this phone is far from satisfactory. It struggles to handle basic tasks smoothly, often lagging and freezing even when navigating through simple apps like messaging or browsing. Opening multiple apps at once is nearly impossible without encountering significant slowdowns.

**Freezing Issues:** The most frustrating aspect of using this phone is its tendency to freeze unexpectedly. Whether I'm trying to send a text message or browse the internet, the phone frequently becomes unresponsive, requiring me to wait several seconds or even restart the device to regain control.

**Calling System:** The calling system on this phone is poorly designed and unreliable. I've encountered numerous issues during phone calls, including dropped calls, distorted audio, and difficulty connecting to the network. This makes having a clear conversation a challenging task.

**Build Quality and Design:** While the design of the phone is sleek and modern, the build quality leaves much to be desired. The materials used feel cheap, and the overall construction does not inspire confidence in durability.

**Battery Life:** The battery life is average at best. With the performance issues and constant freezing, the battery drains quickly, especially when trying to use more demanding applications.

**Value for Money:** Considering the issues I've encountered with this phone, I cannot recommend it based on its current performance. The price point may seem appealing, but the overall user experience is compromised due to the frequent technical problems.

**Final Thoughts:** In conclusion, the phone falls short in terms of performance, reliability, and call quality. While it may be tempting due to its affordability, I would advise looking elsewhere for a more reliable and functional smartphone that better suits your needs. This phone's persistent freezing and subpar calling system make it difficult to justify as a worthwhile purchase.

[{'Reviewer': 'Michael Joseph', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in the United Arab Emirates on 4 June 2024', 'Review': 'Upgrading my old phone oneplus 6t 2018 to oneplus 12 2024 i very love it the smooth oxygen OS, the camera 4k to 8k recording zoom up to 120x the snapdragons 8 gen 3 fastest in 2024 processor, the 5400mah battery with wireless charges and reverse charge, RAM with 12gig + 12gig more of extended memory total of 24gig of RAM, 4years of Android Update and 5years of security patches, i love also the new Gamespace for the oneplus 12 and LTPO Amoled screen and 120hz with Dolby love to watch Netflix and movies in this phone.'}, {'Reviewer': 'Ribu', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in India on 28 May 2024', 'Review': "The OnePlus 12 with 12GB of RAM delivers exceptional performance in daily use. The 12GB LPDDR5X RAM ensures that even with multiple apps open, the phone remains responsive and efficient. The overall user experience is fluid, making it ideal for power users and those who demand high performance from their devices.

Camera: The camera system on the OnePlus 12 is one of its standout features. The triple-camera setup, co-engineered with Hasselblad, provides impressive versatility and quality. The main 50MP sensor captures detailed and vibrant photos, with excellent color accuracy and dynamic range. The ultra-wide 48MP lens is great for capturing expansive landscapes and group shots, maintaining good detail and minimal distortion.The 64MP periscope telephoto lens is particularly noteworthy, offering up to 120x digital zoom. This feature is perfect for capturing distant subjects with surprising clarity. Low-light performance is enhanced by advanced night mode capabilities, which produce clear and detailed images even in challenging lighting conditions. The camera also supports 8K video recording, providing ultra-high-definition video with rich detail.

Battery Life: The OnePlus 12's battery life is robust, easily lasting a full day of heavy use. The 5400mAh battery, coupled with efficient power management, ensures that you won't be left searching for a charger midday. Fast charging capabilities are another highlight, with 100W wired and 50W wireless charging allowing for quick top-ups.

Software: Running on OxygenOS 14, based on Android 14, the software experience is clean and user-friendly. The interface is intuitive, with plenty of customization options to tailor the phone to your preferences. Regular software updates from OnePlus ensure that the device remains secure and up-to-date with the latest features and improvements.

Conclusion: The OnePlus 12 (12GB variant) excels in delivering a premium smartphone experience. Its powerful performance, outstanding camera system, and long-lasting battery make it a compelling choice for anyone looking for a high-end device. Fingerprint sensor is also very good. Whether you're a photography enthusiast, a gamer, or a power user, the OnePlus 12 offers a top-tier experience that is hard to beat.

I recently upgraded from my OnePlus 7 to the OnePlus 12, and I couldn't be happier with my decision, especially considering the significant discounts I received. The total discount amounted to ₹22,500, which included an exchange discount of ₹17,000 for my old phone, an additional discount of ₹3,000, and a bank discount of ₹2,500. This substantial saving made the upgrade even more worthwhile.

The OnePlus 12 offers impressive performance with its advanced hardware and software features. The sleek design, vibrant display, and powerful processor make it a top contender in the smartphone market. The camera system is excellent, providing sharp and clear photos even in low light. Battery life is solid, easily lasting a full day with heavy use, and the fast charging capability is a convenient feature.

One concern I've heard from some users is about the phone's water resistance, specifically that it might not perform well if submerged in water. However, this isn't a significant issue for me as I don't plan to use my phone in such conditions. The OnePlus 12 is still robust and reliable for everyday use.

Overall, I'm extremely satisfied with my OnePlus 12. The excellent discounts I received made it an incredible value, and the phone's performance, design, and features exceed my expectations. If you're considering an upgrade and can take advantage of similar discounts, I highly recommend the OnePlus 12.
Read more"}, {'Reviewer': 'Rajkumar bhattarai', 'Rating': '4.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in the United Arab Emirates on 20 July 2024', 'Review': 'best battery and best price phone'}, {'Reviewer': 'Giriprasath GCS', 'Rating': '4.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in India on 26 February 2024', 'Review': "Truly great product from Oneplus.
This product absolutely nailed in every aspect! You can't really find a fault except some minor shortcoming like visible glue around the ginormous camera ring

Right from the product un boxing it is spectacular. The Flowy emerald variant is just WOW. Matte finish glass but is also slippery. Avoid using without a case
You may keep starting at it multiple times a day so better get a transparent case!

The software is smooth, the camera is good but there's room for improvement. Telephoto, Wide Angle, main camera, everything was given the best lens they can find out there. But the color is inconsistent between lenses so they can work on it.
They have definitely improved selfie camera also, as it performs so good in low light than Oneplus 11. I was truly impressed by selfie quality.

This phone has Haptic feedback that will rival if not better than Apple's haptic. Even when we go from low brightness to high by adjusting the brightness lever the haptic also goes from less to intense vibration!
The haptics feels so good in hand you really need to experience it in person.
(Haptic lovers have a try at nearby showroom and I'm sure you'll choose oneplus 12 right away)

The finishing is so smooth. Camera cut out attracts fingerprint other than that the back is very resistant to fingerprints. Camera lens has no protrusions as it's a single smooth piece of glass so cleaning is easy, also looks good as a single piece.

Battery life: One word - MIND BLOWN 😱
Normal users will get 2+ days of battery life. Even heavy users will get a full day with atleast 20% left. And 100w charging is very quick and cool. I was worried whether device will heat up but it didn't!
5400 Mah is biggest batter from Oneplus on a flagship.
But in 50W wireless charging the device does get warm even in an air conditioned environment.

Oneplus has really done a great job at thermal management. Charging, gaming and the phone doesn't get warm. Only if you try heavy stress test it does get warm.

Phone is huge and won't fit in tiny pocket. Weight is equally distributed but long usage in one hand might feel tiring. After using Oneplys 6 this phone does feel heavy and a bit too big for me during one hand usage. But one hand gesture is easy and quick to use. I would have loved if the weight is 30 to 40 grams less. With case it feels bulky and heavy

DISPLAY: Excellent color reproduction and truly smooth. Touch response is great. Feels buttery smooth and aqua touch is a magic. This is truly a blessing for me as I suffer from wet display issue a lot of times and thanks to who ever thought to implement this tech. 90% of your wet touch issue is gone. Brightness is adequate for outdoors.

Speakers are good. Ever since I got this phone I'm not using my JBL Go speaker. Speakers does great job producing excellent sound. But my quad speakers in tablet with Dolby support does perform better than this.

OxygenOS is smooth even though the old OG version is gone, I'm starting to adapt to this new 'colored' version of OxygenOS too. But missing those tiny oneplus personal touch everywhere.

I'm coming to Op12 after using the OG OP6 and it's a huge leap in every aspect.

IR blaster is a blessing. No more juggling between 4 to 5 remotes on the table for TV, DTH, Home theater, fan & AC. I can control multiple devices using one single remote. Thank you for bringing IR blaster back.

Overall this is a great product. Oneplus has really put in a lot of efforts for this product. Whatever improvements was suggested for OP 11 is implemented here.

50w wireless charging is back... This has USB 3.1... The CMF is great compared to 11. Feels very very premium in hand. Finishing can be better. Even in my phone I noticed glue around camera ring. Some phones even have a small visible gap thru which moisture mey enter.

Also this has better windows phone link integration so you can even use your mobile apps on your PC. Earlier only Samsung S series had this. Now Oneplus also has the feature.

There's no reason for someone not to choose this product except if you prefer compact phone and stock android experience. Best value for money if you use exchange & bank offers.
Read more"}]

About this item
Google Pixel 7 is powered by Google Tensor G2; it’s faster more efficient and more secure with the best photo and video quality yet on Pixel[1]

reviews:
[{'Reviewer': 'Amazon Customer', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Canada on 20 January 2024', 'Review': 'This phone is and excellent phone. I feel most cell phones are a bit overpriced, however that is what one must pay I guess .. it has excellent battery life and a boat load of features..the camera takes amazing pics ! and so far I have nothing bad to say about the phone except the finger print reader sometimes wont read my finger prints.. passcode back up..lol.. would definitely purchase again if I had to.'}, {'Reviewer': 'Mauricio', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Mexico on 9 September 2023', 'Review': 'El teléfono esta excelente, sus cámaras, construcción y sistema operativo son lo mas destacable, el sistema operativo es muy fluido y minimalista, se podría decir que es como el iPhone de Android, todo muy minimalista y fluido. La única diferencia destacable en contra del 7pro además del tamaño, es la falta del telefoto y la diferencia de la pantalla, aunque la verdad para el usuario común la diferencia entre el 2K y el FHD+ es casi imperceptible en una pantalla tan pequeña como lo son las de los smartphones, los 90 hercios y los 120 del pro igual no representan una gran diferencia, así que las únicas grandes adiciones en realidad en contraparte del pro son el tamaño y el telefoto, que dependiendo del usuario que seas el telefoto casi no se usa. Así que si buscas un teléfono compacto y fácil de usar a una mano, y no echas en falta el telefoto, es una excelente opción ante su hermano mayor, por casi la mitad del precio'}, {'Reviewer': 'Roger', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Singapore on 27 October 2022', 'Review': 'Brought to replace old pixel. Value for Money.'}, {'Reviewer': 'Cliente de Amazon', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Mexico on 4 December 2023', 'Review': 'Estaba dudando si comprarlo o no , vengo de una note 10 plus la cuál está súper feliz , este celular lo iba a utilizar para mi trabajo pero le di la oportunidad una semana como mi cel personal y la verdad está muy bien las fotos y videos son muy buenos lo he comparado con iPhone 14 y 15 y no le pide nada en ese apartado .
Hay cosas que si extraño de los galaxy como la pantalla lateral y spen, pero hasta ahorita me a gustado bastante hasta estoy pensando en comprar el pixel 8 o 9 el síguete año .
Lo fui a probar a un concierto y la verdad no me defraudó .'}, {'Reviewer': 'Yudi Narine', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Canada on 7 April 2023', 'Review': "Used to have a Samsung S7 before. Even though that phone is very old, the Pixel 7 is a massive improvement in both the camera and efficiency. It has probably the best phone camera I've ever used. I regret not getting the Pixel 7 Pro to get the telephoto camera.

It has so many Quality-of-Life changes built into the phone that I would've never thought about. Here's some examples:
- It has adaptive charging, which means it calculates the perfect rate to charge the phone so that it can charge to 100% before your next alarm will trigger
- Even though adaptive charging is on by default, it has the option to disable it temporarily so that you can do a quick fast charge if you're in a rush
- It tells you up until what time the phone will last until with the charge left on it
- When you copy something, it has a shortcut button to paste it immediately instead of having to hold down on the screen
- Taking a screenshot and cropping is so much faster

There's a bunch more QoL changes that I can't think of off the top of my head. Also, I realize some of these features might've been developed in earlier models, but it's still nice to have.
Read more"}]

Lo - :
- Viene sin auriculares, algo que a estas alturas es un poco "rata".

- La calidad de la cámara de fotos esta por debajo de las expectativas. En este aspecto, esta mas cerca de la gama baja que media.

Naseri'}, {'Reviewer': 'Laurentplt', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in France on 28 May 2024', 'Review': 'Excellent, reçu en temps et en heure ! la avec ce pixel 💯 Google pfff agréablement surpris de la fluidité, prises de photos. Het toestel nodigt namelijk uit tot veel gebruik, ligt lekker in de hand, makkelijke bediening enz. Echt een misser van Pixel.'}, {'Reviewer': 'Natalia Barba', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Spain on 21 November 2023', 'Review': 'Pros:

Cámara Impresionante: La calidad de la cámara en los teléfonos Pixel nunca deja de sorprender, y el 7a no es una excepción. Las fotos son nítidas y los colores vibrantes, incluso en condiciones de poca luz.

Rendimiento Sólido: Con un procesador eficiente y un rendimiento fluido, el Pixel 7a es capaz de manejar multitareas sin problemas. Las aplicaciones se abren rápidamente, y la experiencia general es ágil.

Actualizaciones Rápidas de Android: Como dispositivo Google, el Pixel 7a recibe actualizaciones de Android de inmediato. Esto asegura que siempre tengas las últimas funciones de seguridad y software.

Duración de la Batería Confiable: La duración de la batería es sólida, proporcionando un día completo de uso sin necesidad de recarga. Esto es especialmente útil para aquellos que están en movimiento constantemente.

Contras:

Diseño Conservador: Aunque la calidad de construcción es buena, el diseño del Pixel 7a puede parecer un poco aburrido en comparación con algunos de sus competidores. Falta el factor "wow" en términos de estética.

Pantalla Mejorable: Aunque la pantalla es de alta resolución, algunos usuarios podrían desear colores más vibrantes y un mejor rendimiento bajo la luz del sol. No es necesariamente un punto débil, pero hay margen para mejoras.

Ausencia de Carga Inalámbrica: En un mercado donde la carga inalámbrica se está convirtiendo en estándar, la falta de esta característica en el Pixel 7a podría decepcionar a algunos usuarios que valoran la comodidad de cargar sin cables.

En resumen, el Google Pixel 7a es una opción sólida, especialmente para aquellos que buscan una experiencia Android pura con una excelente calidad de cámara y actualizaciones rápidas. Sin embargo, podría quedarse un poco atrás en términos de diseño y características premium en comparación con algunos de sus competidores
